# NOTE: src/assetsglb/ (unreferenced 3D-asset experiments that leaked ~125MB
# into the published 2.1.0 tarball) is excluded via a negated entry in
# package.json's "files" array, NOT here — .npmignore has no effect on a path
# once "src/" is already allowlisted by "files" (verified empirically).

